{"parentUuid":"64f36160-0b7f-484e-a20d-20744e3edbd8","isSidechain":false,"message":{"id":"424850ac-aac7-4ec7-bc3d-6227394f0e27","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"deepseek-v4-pro","content":[{"type":"text","text":"测试通过。虽然终端中文显示有乱码，但数值结果正确。\n\n---\n\n## 核心要点总结\n\n### 关键理解\n\n**输入格式**：`z` 的 shape 是 `(2N, D)`，其中 N 是 batch_size。`z[0]` 和 `z[1]` 是一对正样本（同一张图的两个增广），`z[2]` 和 `z[3]` 是一对，以此类推。\n\n```\nz = [img0_aug1, img0_aug2, img1_aug1, img1_aug2, img2_aug1, img2_aug2]\n     └─── 正对 ────┘  └─── 正对 ────┘  └─── 正对 ────┘\n```\n\n### 代码中 6 个步骤\n\n| 步骤 | 操作 | 代码 |\n|------|------|------|\n| 1 | 计算相似度矩阵 | `sim = z @ z.T` |\n| 2 | 除以温度 | `sim = sim / temperature` |\n| 3 | 构造正样本索引 | `pos = arange(N) ^ 1` → `[1,0,3,2,5,4]` |\n| 4 | 抽取正样本相似度 | `pos_sim = sim[i, pos[i]]` |\n| 5 | 计算 log-sum-exp（排除自己） | `logsumexp(sim_no_self, dim=1)` |\n| 6 | InfoNCE = -pos_sim + log_sum_exp | `loss = mean(-pos_sim + log_sum_exp)` |\n\n### 温度 τ 的作用\n\n- **τ → 0**：分布变尖锐，模型拼命拉近正样本、推开困难负样本（可能导致过拟合）\n- **τ → ∞**：分布变平滑，正负样本差别变小（学习信号弱）\n- **典型值**：SimCLR 论文用 `τ = 0.5`（小 batch）或 `τ = 0.07~0.1`（大 batch）\n\n### 在训练循环中使用\n\n```python\n# 假设 data_utils 已经提供了两路增广 x1, x2\ncriterion = NTXentLoss(temperature=0.5)\n\nx1, x2 = batch  # 各 (N, 3, 32, 32)\nz1 = model(x1)  # (N, D)\nz2 = model(x2)  # (N, D)\nz = torch.cat([z1, z2], dim=0)  # (2N, D)，交替排列\nloss = criterion(z)\n```\n\n需要我继续帮你完成 `pretrain.py` 的训练循环吗？"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":623,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":31232,"output_tokens":677,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"type":"assistant","uuid":"38b87ede-fb21-4969-a76a-602cb34c0c21","timestamp":"2026-06-27T11:32:20.919Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"E:\\program_prject\\vscode_python_project\\论文复现\\mini-simclr-assignment