{"parentUuid":"4857463e-7c0c-4249-98b4-caee40282683","isSidechain":false,"message":{"id":"b2f9f22a-c92e-4b46-8c89-e22bb9a2f6e2","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"deepseek-v4-pro","content":[{"type":"text","text":"全部通过。以下是完整实现的文件总结：\n\n---\n\n## 项目文件总览\n\n```\ncode/\n├── model.py          # ✅ Encoder + ProjectionHead + SimCLR 封装\n├── loss.py           # ✅ NT-Xent loss（刚刚实现）\n├── pretrain.py       # ✅ 预训练循环（刚刚实现）\n├── linear_probe.py   # ✅ 线性评估（刚刚实现）\n├── utils.py          # ✅ 工具函数：checkpoint 保存/加载\n└── data_utils.py     # ✅ 数据增强 + CIFAR-10 加载\n```\n\n## NT-Xent Loss 的核心逻辑回顾\n\n```\nz = torch.cat([z1, z2], dim=0)          # (2N, D)\nz = torch.empty(2N, D)\nz[0::2] = z1; z[1::2] = z2             # 交替排列\n```\n\n关键步骤：\n1. **相似度矩阵** → `sim = z @ z.T / τ`\n2. **正样本索引** → `pos = arange(2N) ^ 1`（异或翻转最低位）\n3. **排除自己** → 对角线填 `-inf`\n4. **InfoNCE** → `loss = mean(-pos_sim + logsumexp(sim_no_self))`\n\n## 使用方式\n\n**Step 1 — 预训练：**\n```bash\ncd code && python pretrain.py\n```\n\n**Step 2 — 线性评估：**\n```bash\ncd code && python linear_probe.py\n```\n\n`pretrain.py` 中的 `train_size` 参数可以限制训练集大小（如 5000），方便 CPU 快速验证流程是否跑通。"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":297,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":39040,"output_tokens":394,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"type":"assistant","uuid":"058f512d-0067-4e66-9d96-d620a112fd3c","timestamp":"2026-06-27T11:38:18.476Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"E:\\program_prject\\vscode_python_project\\论文复现\\mini-simclr-assignment-main\\mini-simclr-assignment-main\\code","sessionId":"5ca0762f-62dc-46ac-bae9-80edd8347491","version":"2.1.138","gitBranch":"master"}
